---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Gharbiya STEM Hack Club"
  description="Learn about Gharbiya STEM Hack Club mission, season progress, and impact."
  currentPath="/about"
>
  <section class="surface prose prose-slate max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
    <h1>About Gharbiya STEM Hack Club</h1>
    <p>
      Gharbiya STEM Hack Club is a student-led technology community focused on practical learning, collaboration, and maker culture.
      Our mission is to turn curiosity into shipped work through structured training tracks and high-energy events.
    </p>
    <h2>Season 5 highlights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Current level: <strong>Level 3 (MAX)</strong></li>
      <li>Two successful events already delivered this season</li>
      <li>Four major bootcamps running from February to June</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Community channels</h2>
    <p>
      Follow updates, photos, and videos on Instagram and check project activity on GitHub.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/gh_hackclub/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Instagram</a><br />
      <a href="https://github.com/hack-club-gh" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

